place.name: UPPER VAENOR
place.gazetteerText: Vainor, Upper, township, Llanbadarnfawr par., Cardiganshire, adjacent to Lower Vainor, 1459 ac., pop. 348. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
